17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
18 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
19 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 4019.1 of Title 69, unless there
20 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
21 A. The Oklahoma Department of Transportation shall require a
22 post-installation inspection for any storm pipe that does not pass a
23 structural dead load test prior to installation.
